. . . The best reason for committing loathsome and detestable acts—and
let’s face it, I am considered something of an expert in this field—is
purely for their own sake. Monetary gain is all very well, but it dilutes
the taste of wickedness to a lower level that is obtainable by anyone with
an overdeveloped sense of avarice. True and baseless evil is as rare as
the purest good—and we all know how rare that is . . .

ACHERON HADES
—Degeneracy for Pleasure and Profit